FBIS3-20665 "jpcen002___94013" JPRS-CEN-94-002 Document Type:JPRS Document Title:Science & Technology China: Energy 26 February 1994 POWER NETWORK Big Growth Expected in Hainan Power Industry in 1994 94P60148A Beijing RENMIN RIBAO (OVERSEAS EDITION) in Chinese 26 Feb 94 p 1 94P60148A Beijing RENMIN RIBAO (OVERSEAS EDITION) Language: Chinese Article Type:CSO [Text] This year will see significant growth in Hainan's electric power industry. Plans for the entire year call for the installation of some 400,000 kilowatts in new capacity. In 1994, Hainan's hydroelectric power and water conservance hub, the Daguangba hydropower station, the Nanshan power plant, and other projects will go on stream one after the other, basically easing the energy shortage.
